description.narrative: SCO continued to reach children under five and pregnant lactating women with essential interventions, even in hard to reach areas. Over 68 % of beneficiaries reached were in the highest severity communities. More than 966,622 children under five and pregnant and lactating women were screened for acute malnutrition, with 685,130 children under five and pregnant lactating women and receiving micronutrients. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:19/01/2020
